><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">D1 has told investors who selected a 50-50 mi=
x of public and private assets that the strategy lost 23% through May. The =
firm attributed most of the damage to public investments, which fell 44%. I=
t marked down private assets only 8% -- including 0.05% last month. There=
=E2=80=99s a reason it wasn=E2=80=99t more dramatic: D1 assesses the value =
of its private stakes quarterly, with only some exceptions in the interim. =
The next round is due at the end of this month.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">While D1 will likely mark down some of the companies in its portfolio,=
 its biggest investment, SpaceX, is expected to be marked up by about 25% a=
fter a recent funding round, according to a person with knowledge of the fi=
rm=E2=80=99s thinking.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When valuations turn=
 sharply downward, private markets can take six to nine months to settle on=
 new prices, said Ken Smythe, founder of Next Round Capital, which helps in=
stitutional investors trade such assets. One reason is that sales tend to s=
tall after a plunge, with investors reluctant to lock in losses.</p><p styl=
e=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThe secondary market is in a quandary becaus=
e people can=E2=80=99t figure out what stuff is worth right now,=E2=80=9D S=
mythe said. =E2=80=9CBuyers are demanding lower prices, making liquidity di=
fficult for many of these names.=E2=80=9D Sellers, meanwhile, =E2=80=9Cdon=
=E2=80=99t want to accept the reality of how much less they=E2=80=99re wort=
h now.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you own pub=
lic stocks, you don=E2=80=99t get any choice about accepting that they=E2=
=80=99re worth less: You can look at the price on your screen, and if it=E2=
=80=99s down it's down. If you own private stocks, you can wait a bit. Mayb=
e they=E2=80=99ll go back up!=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhi=
le at the Information, here is =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/28017010.285603/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlaW5mb3JtYXRpb24uY=
