ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> talked</a> about=
 this <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28017010.285=
603/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTItMjE=
